317
00:29:21,386 --> 00:29:31,104
[Drummond] Alternatively and sadly, there have been three contentions reported anonymously which have been investigated and confirmed.

318
00:29:32,773 --> 00:29:33,773
Oh.

319
00:29:33,774 --> 00:29:36,860
"One: uses too many big words."

320
00:29:38,862 --> 00:29:41,322
Well, perchance I may
colloquially employ a...

